# Netlify Redirects for Minishop
# This file ensures that clean URLs (like ukmstore.netlify.app/username) 
# are correctly handled by index.html without a 404 error.

# 1. Allow existing files to be served normally
/auth.html          /auth.html          200
/dashboard.html     /dashboard.html     200
/index.html         /index.html         200
/404.html           /404.html           200

# 2. Redirect all other paths to index.html
# This allows the JavaScript in index.html to parse the shop name from the path
/*                  /index.html         200
